titles.title: To suspend temporarily the duty on Flumetralin Technical - 2-chloro-N-Y2,6-dinitro-4-(tri-fluoromethyl)phenyl?-N-ethyl- -fluorobenzenemethanamine.

bill.summary:
12/18/2007--Introduced.
Amends the Harmonized Tariff Schedule of the United States to suspend temporarily the duty on Flumetralin Technical - 2-chloro-N-Y2,6-dinitro-4-(tri-fluoromethyl)phenyl?-N-ethyl- -fluorobenzenemethanamine.
